        "fontFamily": "Verdana",
        "fontSize": 9,
        "textColor": "#000000",
        "label": "Tables:\n- Wood Costs\t- Purchase Order\n- Posting labor\t- Rates\n- Posting lumber\t- Lumber Species\n- Posting plywood\t- Notes\n- Contacts\t- Pictures\n- Phone numbers\t- Payments\n- Email addresses\t- Letters\n- Addresses\t- Plywood Species\n- Jobs\t- Posting Other\n\n\nFor data import:\n- Clear all table data\n- Go to layout for each table\n- Choose File/Import Records/File...\n- Navigate to the old data file\n- Choose Matching names from Arrange By\n- Choose Import\n- Choose NOT to perform auto-options\n- Change costs in Lumber Posting, Posting Labor and Plywood Posting to number (turn off auto-calculation)\n- Use Records/Relookup to set current rates in today fields\n- Change costs back to auto-calculation",
        "ddrArrangeOrder": 19
      },
      "type": "label"
    },
